text: Zsolt Aubel (born 20 May 1972) is a Hungarian footballer who played for BVSC Budapest as striker. ==References== * Futballévkönyv 1999 [Football Yearbook 1999], Volume I, pp. 78–82, Aréna 2000 kiadó, Budapest, 2000; * Profile, Nela.hu; accessed 16 November 2016.
